                        <h3>ASHABEN CHIKKIWALA</h3>
                         <p>Our dear late founder, Smt. Ashaben Jayeshbhai Shah initiated the business venture of producing and selling of thin crust Chikki from her home in 2001. Her Chikki became so popular that she was known as Ashaben Chikkiwala. Which later became a brand in itself.</p>
                        <p>In the beginning she started making Sing and Til Chikki made of Jaggery. With the increasing demand and gaining popularity she started making various kinds of thin crust Chikki, all made with healthy jaggery and with ingredients like Kopra,Dalia, Black Til, Mix Seeds</p>
