                        <div class="mt-4">Now, the small household venture of Ashaben Shah has gone on to become a big brand name itself as “ASHABEN CHIKKIWALA”. We started and own the company “SATVIK FOOD PRODUCTS”. We continue her rich legacy of making hygienic, fresh, pure products in a traditional way.</div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4">We have introduced among other things, pure whole-wheat flour, hand-roller Khakhara made with pure cow-ghee in 4 flavours. It has been also started under the same name “ASHABEN CHIKKIWALA” We also making seasonal food Product like Dates dryfruit rolls, Methi Pak, Adadiya, Pend, Kachariyu in winter season. </div>
